reviewText: Delivered promptly to Australia. Great opportunity to see the fabulous Barbara in some of her best roles. Never seen before by me  'General Yen', 'Miracle Woman' or the Douglas Sirk 'All I Desire' and , of course, a bonus of her best perforemanc - 'Double Indemnity'. My only regret the package did not include 'Stella Dallas' which I shall now search for.
